    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>shredded kale</strong></span> and cook, covered, for 1 min or until beginning to wilt</p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up, then sit the <strong>haddock bites</strong> over the sauce</p>\n<p>Cook, covered, for 1-2 min further or until the haddock is cooked through</p>\n<p>Note: <span class=\"text-highlight\">Please</span> ensure you cook your fish thoroughly (until piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
