      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Snip</span> the <strong>chives</strong> and<strong> dill</strong> with <strong>scissors</strong></p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>\n<p>Once the fish is cooked, gently stir the <strong>chopped herbs</strong> through the sauce – this is your <strong>herby haddock stew</strong></p>",
